OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,FThis week's Scottish Budget will set
OL,7,Fthe country up to "win big" in the
OL,8,Ffuture, the Finance Secretary has said.
OL,10,FShona Robison will lay out the
OL,11,FScottish Government's tax and spending
OL,12,Fplans in Parliament on Wednesday ` the
OL,13,Ffirst since John Swinney took office.
OL,15,FThe Budget comes against a backdrop of
OL,16,Fdire public finances, somewhat
OL,17,Falleviated by a #3.4 billion increase
OL,18,Fin the next financial year caused by
OL,19,Fthe UK Government's spending decisions
OL,20,Foutlined in October.
