OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,FIt has already been announced the
OL,7,FScottish Budget will allow for a
OL,8,Fdevolved pension age winter heating
OL,9,Fpayment next year, which will give all
OL,10,Fpensioners at least #100 and see those
OL,11,Fworse off receive up to #300.
OL,13,FSpeaking ahead of her Budget
OL,14,Fannouncement to Holyrood, Ms Robison
OL,15,Fsaid the investment in the plans will
OL,16,Fresult in more jobs and "putting more
OL,17,Fmoney into people's pockets", as she
OL,18,Fturned her focus to the long term.
