OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,F"This week we will publish a Budget
OL,7,Fwhich delivers progress for Scotland,
OL,8,Fby Scotland ` laying the foundations
OL,9,Ffor Scotland's long-term success," she
OL,10,Fsaid.
OL,12,F"The First Minister has made clear his
OL,13,Ffocus on delivering on the priorities
OL,14,Fof people across Scotland ` whether
OL,15,Fthat is improving the NHS and other
OL,16,Fpublic services, growing our economy,
OL,17,Ftackling the climate emergency or
OL,18,Feradicating child poverty.
