OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,F"His first Budget will deliver
OL,7,Fprogress on the issues people care
OL,8,Fabout most.
OL,10,F"It is also a Budget for hope, that
OL,11,Fputs in place the investment that will
OL,12,Fset us up to win big in the years to
OL,13,Fcome ` creating more and better jobs,
OL,14,Fputting more money into people's
OL,15,Fpockets and introducing a universal
OL,16,Fpension age winter heating payment.
OL,18,F"It will ensure that we create the
OL,19,Fconditions for every person in
OL,20,FScotland to thrive.
