OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,F"While the UK Government's Budget
OL,7,Ftreated Scotland like an afterthought,
OL,8,Fthis is a Government that will put the
OL,9,Fpeople of Scotland first.
OL,11,F"We have listened carefully to the
OL,12,Fneeds and priorities of organisations
OL,13,Fand businesses across Scotland and
OL,14,Fengaged seriously and constructively
OL,15,Fwith other parties.
OL,17,F"But above all we have listened
OL,18,Fcarefully to the people of Scotland `
OL,19,Fand this is a Budget that will deliver
OL,20,Ffor them."
