OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,FThe Government faces a tough time
OL,7,Fpassing its Budget, however, with a
OL,8,Fdeal required to get it over the line
OL,9,Fand pass the Bill in the new year.
OL,11,FA deal is most likely to be struck
OL,12,Fwith the Scottish Greens ` the SNP's
OL,13,Fformer coalition partners and previous
OL,14,Fpartners in multiple budgets ` or the
OL,15,FScottish Liberal Democrats.
OL,17,FLib Dem leader Alex Cole-Hamilton has
OL,18,Fsaid his four MSPs will not back the
OL,19,FBudget if it includes "one penny" of
OL,20,Fspending on Scottish independence,
OL,21,Fmeaning a deal could anger SNP voters.
