OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,FThe Greens have said they will not
OL,7,Fsupport a budget that cuts funding for
OL,8,Findependence, with co-leader Patrick
OL,9,FHarvie saying his party will not be
OL,10,Faverse to blocking the Budget.
OL,12,FSuch a move could spark a chain of
OL,13,Fevents leading to an early election,
OL,14,For a vote by MSPs to bring forward the
OL,15,F2026 Holyrood poll.
OL,17,FMr Swinney used an address to the
OL,18,FRoyal Society of Edinburgh last week
OL,19,Fto call for collaboration from other
OL,20,Fparties, warning failing to pass the
OL,21,FBudget would cause "disruption".
