OL,3,CBudget will set Scotland up to 'win
OL,4,Cbig' in future, says Robison
OL,6,FScottish Labour finance spokesman
OL,7,FMichael Marra accused the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment of causing "chaos" in the
OL,9,Fpublic finances.
OL,11,F"Tory austerity has provided the SNP
OL,12,Fwith cover for its own failures, but
OL,13,Fnow Labour has turned the page and
OL,14,Fdelivered record levels of funding for
OL,15,FScotland," he said.
OL,17,F"The SNP is out of excuses ` this
OL,18,FBudget must deliver the genuine change
OL,19,Fin direction our country so badly
OL,20,Fneeds."
